- **Keep Nx updated:** Run `nx migrate latest` followed by `nx migrate --run-migrations` to get the latest features and [automated dependency updates](/docs/features/automate-updating-dependencies).
- **Supercharge your CI:** Connect to [Nx Cloud](https://cloud.nx.app/get-started) for remote caching, distributed task execution, and AI-powered CI features — free for small teams.
